developerResponse:
{'id': 12851624, 'body': 'Hi there! Thank you for taking the time to review Affirm on the App Store. We appreciate the feedback and would love to get more information from you to help address your concerns about Affirm. We truly value the feedback of our customers and will take any opportunity to learn from it.

If you have yet to receive the refund to your Affirm loan, we encourage you to contact the merchant for a status update. If the merchant has confirmed the refund was issued please send us your email in the thread for our team to take a closer look! Once you submit your email our team will be sure to follow up with you! Thank you.

-The Affirm Care Team', 'modified': '2020-01-10T21:42:04Z'}
